QuestionTxt: From what you have heard or read, who won the national popular vote this year (2016)--that is, the most votes in the country overall--Hillary Clinton or Donald Trump, or are you unsure?
StudyNote: Interviews were conducted with respondents on landline telephones and cellular phones. The sample includes 40% landline and 60% cell phone respondents.
